    "       \"            sparse_output\\n\",\n",
    "       \"            <span class=\\\"param-doc-description\\\">sparse_output: bool, default=True<br><br>When ``True``, it returns a :class:`scipy.sparse.csr_matrix`,<br>i.e. a sparse matrix in \\\"Compressed Sparse Row\\\" (CSR) format.<br><br>.. versionadded:: 1.2<br>   `sparse` was renamed to `sparse_output`</span>\\n\",\n",
